    public class JDOQLResultQueryParams<T extends PersistableObject,​Q extends javax.jdo.query.PersistableExpression<T>>
extends JDOParameters<T,​Q,​JDOQLResultQueryParams<T,​Q>>
    This class is designed to construct/detail JDOQLTypedQuery to select list of list. Each list item contains values of fields taken from stored objects.
